app.p: The following are available online at https://www.mdpi.com/1660-3397/19/2/95/s1: Figures S1–S8: 1H NMR, 13C NMR, COSY, HSQC, HMBC spectra of tedaniophorbasin A ( 1); Figures S10–S17: 1H NMR, 13C NMR, COSY, HSQC, HMBC spectra of tedaniophorbasin B ( 2).
